    dc:description "FIG. 4. — Alvania isolata (Laseron, 1956): A, B, holotype, height 1.5 mm, Christmas Island, AMS C.102476; C, original drawing; D-F, paratype, height 1.6 mm, Christmas Island, AMS C.102476; G, H, paratype, height 1.6 mm, Christmas Island, AMS C.304689. Images: A. C. Miller; copyright: Australian Museum. Scale bar: 100 mm." ;
