    dc:description "FIG. 18. — Alvania uapou n. sp.:A, B, holotype,height 1.70 mm,Marquesas,Ua Pou,Motu Mokohe,Atelier MARQUISES Stn 20, 10-15 m,MNHN-IM-2000-38710; C-F, paratypes, height 1.70 mm (C), 1.66 mm (D), 1.63 mm (E), 1.57 mm (F), Marquesas, Ua Pou, Motu Mokohe, Atelier MARQUISES Stn 20, 10-15 m, MNHN- IM-2000-38711." ;
