    dc:description "FIG. 19. — Alvania uapou n. sp.: holotype, height 1.70 mm, Marquesas, Ua Pou, Motu Mokohe Atelier MARQUISES Stn 20, 10-15 m: A, shell; B, C, details of the protoconch microsculpture; D, E, details of the teleoconch microsculpture (MNHN-IM-2000-38710). Scale bars: B, C, 100 μm; D, E 20 μm." ;
